    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your<strong> balsamic dressing</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Toss the <strong>salad </strong>in the <strong>balsamic dressing</strong></p>",
